This repository contains games that are useful for both training programming and entertain ourselves.
### USAGE ###
1) animal_draw.py:
	- This is a simple program that allows to make a draw with a given list of items. In this case animals.
	- Command line: python3 animal_draw.py
2) tennis_tournament.py:
	- A program that simulates a tennis tournament of all professional men categories. Plus some additional personalized options.
	- Command line: python3 tennis_tournament.py
3) survival_role.py:
	- A game of role in which you have to survive the different traps and situations that you will choose as you advance.
	- Command line: python3 survival_role.py
